Introduction

Document Purpose

The purpose of this Software Requirements Specification (SRS) is to define and describe the functions and specifications of our project Study Police. It will explain the purpose and features of the system, the interfaces of the system, what the system will do.By reading this SRS document other developers would be able to modify the project if needed.

Product Scope

  • Reading application is an online monitoring system with some good features, an user could know how many time times spend a student for his/her study. User would need to sign up and sign in todo these activities, third party log in system would be available also.

  • This project would be very helpful for those who want to monitoring her students so that the students study properly at home or not. So its easy to track the process.

  • Software Requirements Specification for 'Study Police' Page 2

  • Faculty would get help from this project. He wouldn't need to think for her student for regular studies.

Intended Audience and Document Overview

References and Acknowledgements

Overall Description

Product Overview

This app is developed to track the amount of time users spend to study using this particular application. Instructors can monitor the time and upload study materials. Instructors can also see the total time spent on a lecture by the instructors. The users are able to log in using facial recognition system and the eye tracking system is used to keep the time track. This application is developed to run on Android and IOS.

Product Functionality

Sign Up: Creates a new account.

Log In: Users can log in to his/her accounts.

Create Classroom: Users can create classrooms.

Join Classroom: Users can join classrooms.

Upload Materials: Teachers can upload study materials to the classroom.

Track Students: Teachers can track the amount of time each student has studied.

Student Info: Teachers can view the leaderboard of the students.

Material Info: Teachers can view the list of mostly viewed materials.

Design and Implementation Constraints

Design Constraints:

  • This application will be developed only for mobile devices, so other devices cannot use this application.
  • The application requires a capable camera for facial recognition and eye tracking. So the devices which do not fulfill this cannot use this application.

    Implementation Constraints:

  • There is limited time (10 weeks).
  • There is a limited number of people working on it (3-4 people).

Hardware Interfaces

This application uses an eye tracking API and a facial recognition API which uses smartphone camera for eye tracking and facial recognition.

Software Interfaces

This app can be run on android devices which have version 5.0 (Lollipop) or more.

Functional Requirements

Features

F1: The system shall use eye tracking to determine the amount of time users spent to study using this application. F2: The system shall use facial recognition to determine the identity of the user and update his study time. F3: The system shall perform as an online classroom where teachers can upload materials and students will be able to read the materials.

Other Non-functional Requirements

Performance Requirements

We are going to use an API for tracking the eye for a specific person. For tracking the eye we are also using an webcome that identify for a specific person. User's rating: Users will be able to give rating after taking and enjoying that service.

Safety and Security Requirements

Safety Requirements

As there is a matter of paying money in online by credit card, safety issues could arise. Next developers could add other paying systems for example Bkash, Rocket etc.

Security Requirements

Admin Login Security:

If an admin tries to log in to the web portal with a non-existing account then the admin should not be logged in. The admin should be notified about log-in failure.

Admin Account Security:

An admin and IP address should not be able to log-in to the web portal for a certain time period after three times of failed log-in attempts.

User Account Security:

If a user wants to create an account and the email is occupied, the user should be asked to choose a different email.

Software Quality Attributes

The reliability that the system gives the right booking of the user's choice. Availability: The availability of the system when it is used both in web app and android app. Reusability: The code of the system will be reusable. Maintainability: The application should be easy to extend. The code should be written in a way that it favors implementation of new functions. Portability: The application should be portable by android app and also the domain of web app would be accessible from any part of the world (just internet connection will be needed).
